title: Counter-Strike Source - Maps - FY_ABBOTTABAD [Terrorists] (1080p)
description:
Counter-Strike: Source - fy_abbottabad on Terrorists side (1080p)
Download link: http://www.gamebanana.com/maps/156014


* Map Info *

Creator of the map: Fletch

Based on Osama's compound in Abbottabad, Pakistan. There is a newer version of this map (de_abbottabad): http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xbngkz1zX-o

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------­--------


General info in-game:

* All models are HD (World views). This for the quality of the game, as the standard models are very undetailed.
* AUG (Bullpup) Is the only skin that is not default, but it is the only HD skin I could find that almost matches the original one.
* Desert Eagle and grenades are same model but another skin.
* Both CT's and T's packs are different, they are very highly detailed models. Again because of the poor standard quality
* At last, the in-game options are all highest, except for Anti-aliasing, which is x4 instead of x8 for faster performance.


GAMEPLAY MODE: Fight Yards

* Fight Yards was the first new type of map introduced in Counter-Strike: Source. It features small to medium-sized maps where both teams have to kill each other in order to win. These maps can make most playthroughts very fast, and therefor less boring. The distinction between fy and other maps is that the teams don't have to look for each other while walking miles around a map, neither does it feature a tactical gameplay, you just go and shoot! Good luck!

title: Counter-Strike Source: Maps - MG_CASTLE_V2 (1080p)
description:
Counter-Strike: Source - mg_castle_v2 (1080p)
Download link: http://www.gamebanana.com/maps/102168


* Map Info *

Creator of the map: Slayer, Tomgreen & Solid Snake

mg_castle_v2 is another minigame map that's very funny, and still popular on many mg-servers! This as a classic everyone should have in the map list. Teams are spawned in their respective castle and have to destroy each other before the other team does. This can be achieved by either using the cannons provided at the top of the castles, or directly crossing over the bridge for a bloody knifefight! Your choice, have fun!


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------­--------


General info in-game:

* All models are HD (World views). This for the quality of the game, as the standard models are very undetailed.
* AUG (Bullpup) Is the only skin that is not default, but it is the only HD skin I could find that almost matches the original one.
* Desert Eagle and grenades are same model but another skin.
* Both CT's and T's packs are different, they are very highly detailed models. Again because of the poor standard quality
* At last, the in-game options are all highest, except for Anti-aliasing, which is x4 instead of x8 for faster performance.


GAMEPLAY MODE: Minigame

* mg stands for MiniGame, and is a very pleasing and humorous mod in css. The target is for the CT's to stay alive during the round by staying on platforms that can be physically moved/shot by cannons (Those are been controlled by T's of course). After the time goes up, T's and CT's can fight against each other. In other cases, CT's have free choice to kill the player instantly or to kill him personally. Sometimes, T's get another chance by a second little round where CT's have to escape other type of dangerous tricks, but after that it's over! Have fun!

Download link: http://www.gamebanana.com/maps/155206
Playlist: http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLE6A50F754D876FFD&feature=viewall
● Server IP: N/A


* Map Info *

Creator(s) of the map: GrandOp

A very good map! Very nice, and is moderate to hard in difficulty. Althought this only applies at the end of the map, because there are many zombie choke points at the same time. Good luck anyway!

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------­--------


General info in-game:

* All models are HD (World views). This for the quality of the game, as the standard models are very undetailed.
* AUG (Bullpup) Is the only skin that is not default, but it is the only HD skin I could find that almost matches the original one.
* Desert Eagle and grenades are same model but another skin.
* Both CT's and T's packs are different, they are very highly detailed models. Again because of the poor standard quality
* At last, the in-game options are all highest, except for Anti-aliasing, which is x4 instead of x8 for faster performance.


GAMEPLAY MODE: Zombie Escape

* ze stands for Zombie Escape, and is one of the most funniest mods in css that you can find. The game starts with equal teams in T's and CT's and after 8-10 seconds, one player turns into a zombie and must try to hit other players with his single knife... With a bit of luck, he can already hit 3-5 people in a row, and then the epidemy continiues. Otherwise, you have zombie-hunters, which try to kill the first zombie for a quick win (=boring). Zombies have around 2500-3000 health, players the traditional 100hp. Humans must survive to keep the human race alive, otherwise they will be destroyed for an unending life of torment! Have fun!

title: Counter Strike: Source - Skins
description:
Formerly known as TheFalloutDude1.

Gameplay: James

I really struggled to get all of my skins right. It took me about two months to get all these skins. I'm really picky because I want something visually appealing and something that wouldn't distract me from the gameplay at the same time. (except the M3, cause I wanted something more abstract from the zombies! :D) I think I did it! :D (I did leave out some skins because I couldn't find one that fit my criteria)

All of the skins are from FPSBanana. Unfortunately, when I entered this endeavour, I wasn't thinking of releasing the .rars. You can hunt the specifics down on FPSBanana but that would be time consuming. If there is enough demand, I will upload my entire "CStrike" Folder to a sky drive or something for you to copy and paste. :]

Cookie to the perceptive bastard who can spot the clipping error!

Songs:
Plugged In - Rollz
Get Some - Rollz
(in order of course!)

Intro/Outro Song:
Sierra Leone - Mt. Eden Dubstep

title: Counter-Strike Source: Zombie Escape - ZE_ROOFTOP_RUNAWAY_V1 (1080p)
description:
Counter-Strike: Source - ze_rooftop_runaway_v1 (1080p)
Download link: http://www.gamebanana.com/maps/46921
Playlist: http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLE6A50F754D876FFD&feature=viewall


* Map Info *

Creator(s) of the map: Roger Gargantua

The first of his rooftop runaway maps. It's fun, and gets a lot of pressure when the zombies are right behind you when you try to jump throught windows and over boxes! There are 2 principal ways to escape: Via the rooftops, or via the road which is mainly open space. Choose what you think is the best, and reach the train by time of departure! Have fun!

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------­--------


General info in-game:

* All models are HD (World views). This for the quality of the game, as the standard models are very undetailed.
* AUG (Bullpup) Is the only skin that is not default, but it is the only HD skin I could find that almost matches the original one.
* Desert Eagle and grenades are same model but another skin.
* Both CT's and T's packs are different, they are very highly detailed models. Again because of the poor standard quality
* At last, the in-game options are all highest, except for Anti-aliasing, which is x4 instead of x8 for faster performance.


GAMEPLAY MODE: Zombie Escape

* ze stands for Zombie Escape, and is one of the most funniest mods in css that you can find. The game starts with equal teams in T's and CT's and after 8-10 seconds, one player turns into a zombie and must try to hit other players with his single knife... With a bit of luck, he can already hit 3-5 people in a row, and then the epidemy continiues. Otherwise, you have zombie-hunters, which try to kill the first zombie for a quick win (=boring). Zombies have around 2500-3000 health, players the traditional 100hp. Humans must survive to keep the human race alive, otherwise they will be destroyed for an unending life of torment! Have fun!

- CPU = Intel Core i7 860  @ 2.80GHz

title: como descargar e instalar counter strike source (NUEVO LINK)
description:
Hola amigos,hoy les ensenare a como descargar el counter strike,los parches estan en la carpeta del counter..
este es el link para descargarse el counter strike source: http://depositfiles.com/files/hw4ahy6zr 
Paso 1. extraer el archivo que descargaron. si el archivo que se necesita extraer esta en documentos,probablemente no se les ponga abajo si no en cualquier parte en documentos.
Paso 2. les saldra una carpeta con el nombre del juego,la abren y ahora le dan doble click al archivo que tiene la imagen del counter strike source y que dice setup.
Paso 3. le dan a "run", luego "next", y por ultimo "install". 
Paso 4 (muy importante). en la instalacion probablemente les saldra un error al final que dice que "la instalacion fue interrumpida" como a mi me paso. pero no se preocupen que ya los archivos estan en "archivos de programa". como hago eso,pues van a "mi pc", luego a "disco local" y luego a "archivos de programa" y buscan la carpeta que tenga el nombre del juego. si no les sale pues lo vuelven a instalar hasta que les salga. ami me salio a la primera pero como me salio ese error no me daba cuenta de que ya estaba instalado y tenia la carpeta en archivos de programa.
Paso 5. ahora para que lo puedan jugar tendran que instalar los parches. como ven la carpeta del css (counter strike source) esta con pocos archivos, la que les estoy hablando es la carpeta instalada. ahora para que tenga bastantes y les sirva el juego tendran que dirigirse a la carpeta que fue extraida,a la primera en donde esta el "setup". ya en la carpeta,hay otra ahi mismo que dice "parches", la abren y les saldra 3 archivos, primero instalen el que dice "v1" que es el que esta de primero. le dan doble click y le dan "run". luego next, otra vez next y buscan la carpeta del counter strike source que fue la que instalaron y que esta en archivos de programa. la seleccionan y le dan next,y por ultimo install. este es el archivo que mas pesa asi que de seguro se les demore un poco. ahora vamos con el segundo archivo que dice "v17",hacen lo mismo que el parche anterior,solo que esta vez ya no tienen que buscar la carpeta del juego,pero sin embargo si no esta la buscan y lo instalan. este ya es un poco mas liviano haci que se les demora como 5 segundos. ahora vamos con el que dice "v18", hacemos lo mismo que hicimos con los dos anteriores. tienen que hacerlo a ese orden o si no no les funcionara. y bueno,ya casi esta terminado,y como ven,la carpeta de counter strike source ya tiene mas archivos,pero ahora para jugar el juego,esta fue la parte mas confusa para mi ya que no encontraba el archivo ya que el que es del juego dice 40kb, es el que tiene una personita caminando,le dan doble click y ya podran jugar! bueno amigos,eso a sido todo,espero que disfruten el juego,chao.

title: Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (2012) | gameplay HD
description:
Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS: GO) возродит тот ураганный командный игровой процесс, впервые представленный еще 12 лет назад.

CS: GO будет включать в себя новые карты, персонажей, оружие и их улучшенные версии из классической CS (de_dust и т.п.). Кроме того, CS: GO будет содержать новые игровые режимы, систему организации матчей, глобальные таблицы игроков и многое другое.
«Counter-Strike была сюрпризом для игровой индустрии, когда не особо удачный мод стал одним из самых популярных шутеров в мире сразу же после его релиза в Августе 1999 года, — говорит Даг Ломбарди из Valve, — за прошедшие 12 лет, она все еще одна из самых популярных в мире игр, часто появляется на игровых соревнованиях и продана в количестве более 25 миллионов копий по всему миру. CS: GO обещает возродить знаменитый игровой процесс Counter-Strike и предложить его игрокам не только на ПК, но и на консолях следующего поколения и компьютерах Mac».

CS: GO разрабатывается Valve в сотрудничестве с Hidden Path Entertainment. Посетителям выставок «PAX Prime» и «Eurogamer Expo» представиться шанс опробовать игру уже в этом году, а ее выход запланирован на начало 2012 года.

title: Tradução de texto e vozes de Player e Bot Counter Strike CS
description:
Agora ficou mais fácil e divertido jogar Counter Strike, pois a série original do GAME vem em INGLÊS. Com o Tradutor do Counter Strike, é possivel traduzir 100% o game, desde textos do MENU até as vozes dos PERSONAGENS, esse programa tradus todos os MENUS  e  LEGENDAS do GAME, ficando realmente mais facíl e compreensível entender o que se passa durante o jogo. Com o jogo traduzido você vai conseguir intender a comunicação que os Bot's fazem pelo RÁDIO, pois na versão original do jogo eles falam em inglês e só entende quem tem um bom domínio do idioma, sem contar que fica um pouco confuso entender na correria durante o ROUND. Facilita também nas configurações, por que configurar o (keyboard) 'TECLADO'  não é nada fácil pra quem não entende muito de inglês, sendo que após instalar o tradutor você vai ver a diferença na facilidade e o melhor, sem ter medo de mudar alguma coisa no menu sem querer. O CS Tradutor é compatível com CS 1.6 e Condition Zero, e o melhor é que você não precisa perder tempo com instalações longas e com programas que dão problema no seu game, nem vai alterar nada na LISTA de FIND SERVER, como fazem alguns tradutores por aí... o Tradutor é bem simples e fácil de instalar, e não precisa entender muito de programa, pois o CS TRADUTOR faz tudo pra você.

title: Counter Strike Source - Zombie Escape + random stuff
description:
When I had played Zombie Escape for the first time, I realized that I wanted to make a video of it. This is just supposed to show the gameplay, and the fun of playing Counter Strike Source. I combined it with some additional footage I recorded from other servers, and ended up with this.

The part from 0:42 is actually not Counter Strike Source, it's from ''Garry's Mod''. Though the background was the Counter Strike map: ''cs_assault'', and the guy I kicked looks exactly the same as one of the counter terrorist units. You see, I just had to show the ''This. Is. SPARTA!'' kick.

title: Counter-Strike Beta 1.0 - CS_Mansion
description:
Here's a video showing off CS_Mansion in Beta 1.0. I couldn't find a way to quickly suicide in this level, so you won't see me kill myself at the end of the video.

Differences:

- The interior is much more primitive-looking than the final version.  Outside of the front room, everything is different. 

- There's no basement area.

- The sewer passage look much more primitive and connects the CT spawn area to the back of the house instead of the final's basement.

- On the left side of the house is a door that leads inside. This was removed.

- There are two cameras near the CT spawn point.

-The actual CT spawn point looks much more basic. It doesn't look like a road.

- There's a strange house on the left side of the yard.

- Most importantly, there's no button that plays a ring sound near the front door.

title: Counter-Strike Source: Zombie Escape - ZE_MIRROR'S_EDGE_V2_FIX4 (1080p)
description:
Counter-Strike: Source - ze_mirror's_edge_v2_fix4 (1080p)
Download link: http://www.gamebanana.com/maps/146395
Playlist: http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLE6A50F754D876FFD


* Map Info *

Creator(s) of the map: Dark Arrow & Trankimazin

This updated version of ze_mirror's_edge_v2 has mostly focused on repairing (all) the glitches players used to get faster to the finished (Like I did in the v2_video). That's impossible now, and personally that's the best way because otherwise too many players did not get the chance to get there in time! However, what I truly dislike in this update is that there's still the fall-to-death-bug at the elevator part. It's pretty much impossible to find out what's causing the dying players; but I presume it's when they fall onto a weapon (which is a prop_physics) and as such is not built to prevent falling damage. If I were to update teh map, I would simpky place a poll of water there. Anyway, it's still as fun as it is, so have fun!

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------­--------


General info in-game:

* All models are HD (World views). This for the quality of the game, as the standard models are very undetailed.
* AUG (Bullpup) Is the only skin that is not default, but it is the only HD skin I could find that almost matches the original one.
* Desert Eagle and grenades are same model but another skin.
* Both CT's and T's packs are different, they are very highly detailed models. Again because of the poor standard quality
* At last, the in-game options are all highest, except for Anti-aliasing, which is x4 instead of x8 for faster performance.


GAMEPLAY MODE: Zombie Escape

* ze stands for Zombie Escape, and is one of the most funniest mods in css that you can find. The game starts with equal teams in T's and CT's and after 8-10 seconds, one player turns into a zombie and must try to hit other players with his single knife... With a bit of luck, he can already hit 3-5 people in a row, and then the epidemy continiues. Otherwise, you have zombie-hunters, which try to kill the first zombie for a quick win (=boring). Zombies have around 2500-3000 health, players the traditional 100hp. Humans must survive to keep the human race alive, otherwise they will be destroyed for an unending life of torment! Have fun!


My Computer:

- Operating System = MS Windows 7 Home Premium 64-bit SP1
- CPU = Intel Core i7 860  @ 2.80GHz
- RAM = 8,00 GB Dual-Channel DDR3 @ 666MHz (9-9-9-24)
- Motherboard = Gigabyte Technology Co., Ltd. P55A-UD3 (Socket 1156)

title: [VidéoTest] Counter-Strike Global Offensive BETA [PC]
description:
Nom : Vidéo-test de la BETA de Counter-Strike : Global Offensive [PC]
Durée : 15min15sec
Date de Sortie prévue : 1er trimestre 2012
Éditeur : Valve
Développeur : Valve
Genre : FPS
Classification : 16+
Site officiel de l'éditeur : http://www.valvesoftware.com/

Test réalisé par Radiax pour le site Actu-Lan : http://www.actu-lan.com/

Pour ce nouveau vidéo test, je m'attaque à la BETA fermé de Counter-Strike Global Offensive, le prochain titre du studio Valve. Uniquement disponible sur PC, cette BETA fermée démarre bien et semble stable. Malheureusement, seul 7 armes déjà présentes dans les précédents opus, deux maps et quelques nouveautés sont jouables. Peu de contenu donc pour cette BETA, mais une chose est sure, le jeu s'annonce très bon et promet d'intenses batailles entre fans et pro de la série qui à déjà séduit des millions de personnes. Je ne peut donc pas avoir un avis fixe mais j'ai hate de découvrir le jeu dans sa version finale ! Un jeux à suivre de près.
Afin de mieux progresser dans les tests suivant, merci de bien vouloir commenter cette vidéo. Toute remarque est donc la bienvenue, qu'elle soit positive ou négative. Merci.

title: Kaleidoscope (Counter Strike:Source)
description:
MERRY SNOWMAN AND HAPPY SANTA EVERYONE! PLEASE READ BELOW(!)

I'm sorry that I didn't bring you the "huge clip" as I promised you.. I've been insanely busy with preparations for my final exams @ school.
Plus I've tried to be with my family as much as possible during these christmas weeks. This edit was put together in 4 days, and it's containing a shitload of betas, so the quality is not really awesome.. rofl - bare with me.
I thought I'd rather get you something shitty than not getting you anything at all, so here you go. To sooth your pain, I've 2 rather positive announcements to share with you!

1) I've been planning a project with one of the biggest legends in Counter Strike:Source history; RattlesnK. I'll be making a playermovie about him and his career.
It'll be between 5 and 30 minutes long(fucked up, right?) yea. He has shitloads of lan footage as well, but most of it is capped directly from TV, and I don't know whether or not I am allowed to use it in the film, as theres watermarks from the TV programs etc.

2) COMPETITIONS!?
Fuck yes, my SteelSeries competition is still up and running - In fact, ONLY 6 entries are in my entry folder yet. Go watch the video for mor info(415$ PRIZING!!)
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mzcGgSRSRpg

Second of all, yesterday I launched a small competition in the 23rd episode. The winner of that is: flixxn, who was the first to guess "kasper and trobo". Congrats, you'll get your BO account as soon as you PM me! :)



WHATS LEFT TO SAY?
2011 has been an incredible year. Coming from a 2010 with major fuckups in several prods(eh..), flagged videos and accounts hacked - 2011 has been AMAZING!
I went from 3k to +14k subs in 2011, and in August, I even got my partnership - now, I'm partnered on 3 channels, and its going really well!
Artists Universe got founded, closed and now, we're back - stronger than ever! :)

Thanks for everything guys, I couldn't have done a single of these things without you, the support you've given me has been incredible - let's continue in 2012, shall we?
As a Christmas present for you guys, I want you to tell me: What do you want to see in 2012? A certain project? A genre? New stuff - what kind? Let me know - I'll do my best to fulfill your wishes :)

MUSIC:

Peace out, and merry Christmas!

title: Counter Strike Condition Zero Deleted Scenes HD Gameplay Walkthrough Mission 12 (Final) - Rise Hard
description:
Difficulty : Hard
Recorded : 27/12/11
Mission 12 - (19:40HOURS/Belfast, Northern Ireland)

Counter Strike Condition Zero Deleted Scenes
Developer: Ritual Entertainment
Released: Valve Corporation

Plot
A group of political radicals has taken over a high rise building. In addition to holding many hostages, this group plans to detonate a nuclear device in next two hours. The player must enter the high rise without being detected by the terrorists. The terrorists are armed to the teeth and have a nuclear device on their hands, planning to detonate it, regardless of demands and such, in two hours. Since the SAS doesn't wait two hours for shooting people, the player is sent in already under fire to disarm the threat.

title: Counter-Strike Global Offensive - Menu Theme
description:
The Counter Strike Menus theme ;D

Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS: GO) is an online first-person shooter based game currently in development by Valve Software and Hidden Path Entertainment, who also co-developed Counter-Strike: Source. It is the fourth game in the Counter-Strike franchise, excluding Counter-Strike: Neo and Counter-Strike: Online.

Global Offensive is targeted for release in early 2012. It will be available for Microsoft Windows, Mac OS X, Xbox 360 via the Xbox Live Arcade and PlayStation 3 via PlayStation Network. It will feature classic content, such as old maps, as well as brand new maps, characters and game modes. Also, it will support matchmaking and leaderboards. The PlayStation 3 version will offer three control methods, which include using either the DualShock 3 controller, PlayStation Move or USB keyboard/mouse.

title: Counter-Strike: Global Offensive New Right-Eye Peek Advantage
description:
I think most people familiar with Counter-Strike: Source know that in CSS you have an advantage when peeking something to your left.  Everyone calls it the left-eye peek.  You can see more of a person who is peeking out from their right side if you are peeking out from the left.

In CS:GO, the same advantage exists, and appears to be pretty much identical as far as how much exposure their is.  However, in CS:GO the advantage goes to the player peeking from the right.

Not a huge deal, but obviously means some adjustments for people with quick peaks taking sites who were used to things being the other way around.

Pardon the quality, and you can't hear me talk, but you can hear him explain how much of me is visible.  I'll link to the Screenshots when i have time to find them again.

description:
Difficulty : Hard
Recorded : 25/12/11
Mission 3 - Secret War (13:24HOURS/North East Russia

Counter Strike Condition Zero Deleted Scenes
Developer: Ritual Entertainment
Released: Valve Corporation

Plot
The mission begins with the player accompanying several Spetsnaz troops in a Russian APC while the officer gives a briefing: You're heading to disarm a missile silo. Suspiciously, it lost radio contact for the past 24 hours. The officer assumed that the comm system failed.

After attempting to open the doors using a security code, one of the soldiers, Yuri, uses a RC bomb to open the jammed entrance. It is later found out that the base is on emergency power. The player is sent to turn the power generators on. After exploring mysteriously empty areas, the player enters a room of executed scientists, at which your commander lets you know that two different terrorist factions are fighting one another, and the Spetsnaz operatives, for control of the missile silo.

The player is ordered to cover the official's escape, then go back on the offensive to eliminate the terrorists. At the end, the terrorist leader takes a schoolgirl hostage, forcing the player to shoot carefully.

Краткое описание:
1) Скачиваем hlds update tool - ( https://support.steampowered.com/kb_article.php?p_faqid=638 )
2) Создаем сервера папку в C диске туда устанавливаем hlds update tool
3) В cmd вписываем:
C:\Server\HldsUpdateTool.exe -command update -game valve -dir C:\Server
4) После того как скачало вписываем это:
C:\Server\HldsUpdateTool.exe -command update -game cstrike -dir C:\Server
5) Теперь скачиваем Admin Pack ( http://eproxs.net/downloads.php?cat_id=1 )
6) Распаковываем в сервера папку
7) Запускаем сервер

title: How to turn off Mouse Acceleration in Counter Strike (Steam)
description:
Mouse Acceleration instructions:
How to turn off Mouse Acceleration in Counter Strike.

Step 1:

Go to your Steam Library.
Step 2: 
Right click on your Counter Strike game.
Step 3:
Click on Properties.
Step 4:
Click on Set Launch options
Step 5: 
Fill in the box: -noforcemaccel -noforcemparms -noforcemspd
Step 6:
Click on "ok" and you're finished! :)

title: GameFrag- Como entrenar en un DeathMatch - Counter Strike
description:
Para empezar vamos a ver 1 demo de kHRYSTAL en dust2 que la pueden descargar en el siguiente link:

http://www.readmore.de/index.php?cont=demos&id=25998

* Si no tienen cuenta se crean una. ( obvio ).

Ahora analizaremos la demo: 

Cual es el objetivo de kHRYSTAL en este DM, fijense como el va buscando solamente el HS tranquilamente de 1 bala, siquiera es un clicking, es solo ir siguiendo al objetivo y no perderlo. 

Bueno esta forma de entrenar es como el paso 1 de nuestro entrenamiento diario. 

Al jugar de esta forma 1 mapa entero o 2 si es necesario, nos aseguramos que nuestros drags ( movimientos del mouse ), sean lo mas perfectos posibles. hasta que no estemos "marcando" bien a los objetivos seguiremos haciendo esto.

Para el paso 2 empezaremos acelerando el ritmo, cuando ya estemos marcando bien a nuestros oponentes jugaremos como edward que se ve un poco mas desordenado, pero igualmente sigue manteniendo ese ritmo de disparo que es el que ocuparemos en partidos, la demo la pueden descargar aca:

http://www.navi-gaming.com/view_demo.php?id=46&l=en


Punto importante todo esto tiene que ser con AK47. los primeros 2 pasos. 

Ahora un resumen de que debemos hacer.

1.- Entrenar marcar a los oponentes con calma apuntando tal como kHRYSTAL.
2.- Acelerar el clicking tal como lo hace edward. 
3.- empezar a recoilear a los oponentes de mediana distancia.

title: Counter-Strike Source: Zombie Escape - ZE_NUKE_V1 (1080p)
description:
Counter-Strike: Source - ze_nuke_v1 (1080p)
Download link: http://www.gamebanana.com/csszm/maps/148255
Playlist: http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLE6A50F754D876FFD


* Map Info *

Creator(s) of the map: Obscuri (Original author(s): Valve)

This familiar map has turned out to be a zombie escape map too, making it one of the few (still playable/played ones) 'pre-made' zombie escape maps. It doesn't appear to be often at the top vote, but it has more chance than other ones simply because it is a fully working map, and people tend to like familiar maps. It is a tensionated map actually, with some really 'hot' choke points. The only major downside is the very unclear ending. The truck seems to be too slow with the result that many player who are still standing in the truck will die (because the truck is still in the trigger_hurt which kills all players). All-in-all a good all-round map, but only once in a while. Have fun!

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------­--------


General info in-game:

* All models are HD (World views). This for the quality of the game, as the standard models are very undetailed.
* AUG (Bullpup) Is the only skin that is not default, but it is the only HD skin I could find that almost matches the original one.
* Desert Eagle and grenades are same model but another skin.
* Both CT's and T's packs are different, they are very highly detailed models. Again because of the poor standard quality
* At last, the in-game options are all highest, except for Anti-aliasing, which is x4 instead of x8 for faster performance.


GAMEPLAY MODE: Zombie Escape

* ze stands for Zombie Escape, and is one of the most funniest mods in css that you can find. The game starts with equal teams in T's and CT's and after 8-10 seconds, one player turns into a zombie and must try to hit other players with his single knife... With a bit of luck, he can already hit 3-5 people in a row, and then the epidemy continiues. Otherwise, you have zombie-hunters, which try to kill the first zombie for a quick win (=boring). Zombies have around 2500-3000 health, players the traditional 100hp. Humans must survive to keep the human race alive, otherwise they will be destroyed for an unending life of torment! Have fun!

title: The Ancient Counter-Strike Flash Video Collection (2000-2003)
description:
I had to remove the audio of The Beatles - Hello Goodbye ending song in Counter-Stick 1, this song banned the video for over 4 years. Currently the video is not viewable in the US and Denmark due to other songs, but it's a compromise I had to accept, maybe in the future the viewing rights will change again.

This epic three hour collection of ancient Counter-Strike flashmovies will bring you back to the good old times of the internet, before Social Media ruined everything.

This is a collection of old Counter-Strike flashes from the year 2000-2003. The flashes were taken from several sites, such as CStoons, CSnation, CScentral, CSbanana and Newgrounds.

Making this compilation together with my own animations took me about 1 1/2 weeks of non-stop work. 
I take no credit for any of the flashes inside the collection. The only things I created myself were: Intro, Outro, Credits and a new explosion. 

The other stuff I did though was massive editing, resyncing of sound and converting. See below for additional info.

I made some modifications to the following parts:

-RzE introduction video: I added music to this flash, as it had no sound what so ever.
-Casino scene: I added new sound effects to the CT part, as it had almost no sound.
-Counter-Tom: Cut the super-annoying, overly long shooting sequence down to a minimum.
-The "Live Well" flash had a convertion problem, I tried to fix it but it's much slower than it should be. (EDIT: This flash is broken, it's completely black. Probably another video conversion problem)
-I added a new handmade explosion effect for RzE's dance. (It was previously a flashbang effect, eventhough the grenade said HE on it)
-RzE Jeepathon2k: I replaced the hamster dance music at the end of the flash with a new sound that fits the situation better.
-CS school: Added coughing in one part to the almost silent flash.
-CS punchout: Added an old computer (ATARI ST) loading sound.

This video is also used to be on VEOH: http://www.veoh.com/watch/v62935502H5XcFrmJ

title: Counter-Strike Source: Zombie Escape - ZE_MINECRAFT_V1_NM_PF [PlagueFest] (1080p)
description:
Counter-Strike: Source - ze_minecraft_v1_nm_pf (1080p)
Download link: Unavailable for download (Only on the PlagueFest zombie escape server)
Playlist: http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLE6A50F754D876FFD


* Map Info *

Creator(s) of the map: TheGregster101

ze_minecraft_v1_nm_pf is a slightly modified version, specifically created for PlagueFest. The only thing they changed is the music in the background were there was a lot of complaint about. Have fun!

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------­--------


General info in-game:

* All models are HD (World views). This for the quality of the game, as the standard models are very undetailed.
* AUG (Bullpup) Is the only skin that is not default, but it is the only HD skin I could find that almost matches the original one.
* Desert Eagle and grenades are same model but another skin.
* Both CT's and T's packs are different, they are very highly detailed models. Again because of the poor standard quality
* At last, the in-game options are all highest, except for Anti-aliasing, which is x4 instead of x8 for faster performance.


GAMEPLAY MODE: Zombie Escape

* ze stands for Zombie Escape, and is one of the most funniest mods in css that you can find. The game starts with equal teams in T's and CT's and after 8-10 seconds, one player turns into a zombie and must try to hit other players with his single knife... With a bit of luck, he can already hit 3-5 people in a row, and then the epidemy continiues. Otherwise, you have zombie-hunters, which try to kill the first zombie for a quick win (=boring). Zombies have around 2500-3000 health, players the traditional 100hp. Humans must survive to keep the human race alive, otherwise they will be destroyed for an unending life of torment! Have fun!

title: Les graphismes de Counter-Strike : Global Offensive
description:
Voici une mise au point sur les graphismes de la béta de CS:GO dans son état actuel (mi-mars).
Ce ne sont que des observations personnelles, je dis peut-être quelques erreurs, mais globalement l'idée est là.

Cette vidéo n'abordant que l'aspect technique des graphismes, je ne parle pas du travail apporté par les level-designers, mais on voit qu'avec la mise à jour d'hier soir (apportant cs_itly et de_stmarc), la qualité du mapping s'est elle aussi grandement améliorée.

CS:GO est donc pour moi un jeu tout à fait actuel, à la hauteur des opus d'aujourd'hui.

Si vous aimez la vidéo, n'hésitez pas à la partager autour de vous !

title: Counter Strike: Global Ofenssive - Mieszane uczucia
description:
Im dłużej bawię się w Counter Strike: Global Offensive, tym więcej nabieram wątpliwości do tego tytułu. Zaczynam sobie zadawać pytanie dla kogo ta gra jest. Dla nowych graczy? Nie bardzo, stara mechanika, toporne sterowanie i długi czas oczekiwania na odrodzenie. Dla starych graczy? Też niespecjalnie. Oni mają przecież 1.6 i kilka innych wersji old schoolowego Counter Strike'a.
Ciężko mi zatem odpowiedzieć na pytanie czemu ta gra powstaje. Jasne mam jakiś sentyment oglądając stare mapy w nowej odsłonie graficznej, ale żaden sentyment nie zastąpi emocji jakie daje mi Battlefield, czy nawet niespecjalnie doceniany Medal of Honor.

Poprzedni Counter Strike: Global Offensive
http://youtu.be/gCWzDbHwblQ

To miasto jest za małe dla nas... szesnastu
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p37D4a94LO4

title: Мэддисон и Хованский в CS (Counter Strike)
description:
ПОДПИШИСЬ, ЧТОБЫ НЕ ПРОПУСТИТЬ НОВЫЕ ВИДЕО: http://youtube.com/user/russianstandup?sub_confirmation=1

Всем привет, дамы и господа! С вами Юрий Хованский ака МС Хованский - видеоблогер, гангстер и алкоголик, автор таких шоу как "Шаверма Патруль", Russian Stand-Up и "Бич Закупка". Вы можете помнить меня по состоявшемуся батлу с Лариным, несостоявшемуся батлу с Моргенштерном и клипу "Батя в здании". Сейчас у меня на канале выходят разговорные ролики, скетчи, критические обзоры на блогеров, рецепты со Славным Друже, стендап, байки и многое другое. В лучшие моменты карьеры я судил Версус и разрывал тренды, а теперь просто стараюсь не унывать: пишу диссы, снимаю клипы, режиссирую фильмы и постоянно пытаюсь придумывать для вас что-то новое. Мне будет очень приятно, если вы нажмёте на "колокольчик" и подпишетесь на все мои соцсети, чтобы ничего не пропустить.

description:
UPDATED]: More Links Have been added + Patch v42.1

Release 16.6.2011

System Requirements:
- Minimum: 500 mhz processor, 96mb ram, 16mb video card, Windows 2000-XP-Vista-7
- Recommended: 800 mhz processor, 128mb ram, 32mb+ video card, Windows XP-Vista-7

Features:
- Clean rip from Steam
- No modifications, except where noted.
- Protocol 48
- Playable on LAN and Nonsteam Servers
- Half-Life is Included
- Steam Account is not required.
- RevEmu 9.85
- Dedicated Server

Modifications:
- CZ Bots added
- Original models instead of CZ ones.
- Uses Setti masterserver for a list of nonsteam servers

FAQ:
When trying to join a server I get -STEAM validation rejected-
Server isn't cracked or is misconfigured

-The Server is using an older protocol (47) than your client (48).- error when joining a server.:
Ask the admin of the server to update their server or to use dual protocol.

When I'm trying to join a game, the loading bar appears, but while loading,
the game crashes.
You may have an old computer or an onboard GFX. Delete the -userconfig.cfg- file located in the -cstrike- folder.Switch to Direct3D render mode and it should be working.

How I can open the console?
Press ~

How I can get a FPS Counter?
cl_showfps 1 or net_graph 1 (more advanced)

I'm getting visual artifacts while playing
Try updating your video drivers.

Why I can't see my server on LAN?
It's a revEmu bug, on some computers it works, some it doesn't. Try connecting via the LAN ip.

I WANT MY FAVORITESS AAARGH
Download the patch! :D

The game crashes with SteamStartup(0xf,0x0018F928) Failed with error 180: the local Steam Service is not running, when I wry to change my resolution in game.
It's not a problem in the game, It's a problem in the revEmu we are using. Just restart the game and it should work. If it doesn't, edit the Counter-Strike.bat in the game folder and add:

--w 800 -h 600-

(Just replace it with desired resolution)

Source: http://forum.digitalpowered.net/index.php?showtopic=40886

title: Tuto Counter Strike - Guide sur le recul
description:
http://www.millenium.org/
Abonnez vous à la chaîne de PgunMan:
http://www.youtube.com/user/PgunMan
Aide à la visée. Voilà un concept bien étrange, a-t-on besoin de béquilles quand on est dans la force de l'âge et qu'on est en pleine possession de ses moyens ? La paire de lunettes est elle une nécessité quand on a 10/10 à chaque œil ? L'utilisation de l'arme dans un FPS est le principe fondateur du genre, mais c'est la façon dont elle va être utilisée qui va définir la force de frappe d'un joueur ou d'une équipe. Chacune de celles-ci réserve son lot de surprise, une cadence de tir mollassonne ou au contraire frénétique, des effets dévastateurs mais peu précis ou un impact chirurgical mais mais une puissance en dessous des attentes, tout revêt une importance primordiale quand on associe son talent à la forme de jeu que l'on essaie de développer. Dans l'optique didactique qu'on lui connait, PgunMan nous revient aujourd'hui avec un nouvel épisode de son tutoriel Counter Strike et comme à son habitude il est accompagné par le nexux6 Pepito Bleu.

 

 

 

Comme vous l'avez deviné l'épisode du jour est consacré au recul des armes, de ce jeu horizontal ou vertical qu'il faut compenser pour pouvoir tirer parti au maximum du potentiel de ces dernières. Pgunman met en scène ses essais de tous les guns de Counter Strike 1.6 et nous livre ainsi son avis sur la fonction déterminante du recul dans les segments de jeu à courte ou moyenne distance. Si vous pensiez que FPS rimait uniquement avec spamming de la touche de tir, il s'avère que vous vous trompiez grandement. La finesse d'un jeu comme Counter Strike découle aussi de la façon dont vous arrivez à dompter vos armes, si vous avez un fauve enragés entre les mains, il vous desservira à coup sûr et vous mettra en fâcheuse posture. Un nouvel épisode du tutos CS 1.6 toujours aussi intéressant, la correction du tir entérinant un processus ou précision et efficacité se tirent la bourre en filigrane derrière le discours des deux acteurs de la vidéo. À très bientôt pour un nouvel épisode de notre série dédiée à l'univers d'1.6.

title: Counter-Strike: Condition Zero Deleted Scenes - Walkthrough Mission 3 - Secret War
description:
You are a Russian Spetsnaz in an ICBM launch site in North East Russia where the nuke is being fought over between two terrorist forces, the Phoenix Connexion and the Arctic Avengers. 

Overview:
Rebels have taken over a remote missile complex in Russia. The threat of nuclear war looms. It is crucial that the facility is reclaimed and that the warhead is disarmed.

Objectives:
Locate the nuclear missle silo.
Disarm the Nuke.
Escort all facility support staff from the silo complex

My walkthrough for Counter-Strike: Condition Zero Deleted Scenes, a singleplayer expansion to Counter-Strike: Condition Zero. Condition Zero and the Deleted Scenes comes bundled with the original GoldSrc Counter-Strike on Steam for $9.00. I don't think you can have one without the other. BTW this is still GoldSrc, the Half-Life 1 engine.

title: Counter-Strike: Condition Zero Deleted Scenes - Walkthrough Mission 4 - Building Recon
description:
British SAS fighting against Arctic Avengers for a nuke hidden inside a Warehouse Comples in Ventspils, Latvia. This is my least favorite mission in the game.

Overview:
Unconfirmed information places a terrorist group inside this warehouse complex. It is also suspected that this group has immediate hostile intentions and possesses a nuclear warhead.

Objectives:
Infiltrate the complex.
Verify the existence of the nuclear bomb.
Eliminate any opposition.

My walkthrough for Counter-Strike: Condition Zero Deleted Scenes, a singleplayer expansion to Counter-Strike: Condition Zero. Condition Zero and the Deleted Scenes comes bundled with the original GoldSrc Counter-Strike on Steam for $9.00. I don't think you can have one without the other. BTW this is still GoldSrc, the Half-Life 1 engine.

Buy the game here:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/80/

http://www.mediafire.com/?vxrhpxtmhg0mtl0



Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS: GO) will expand upon the team-based action gameplay that it pioneered when it was launched 12 years ago.

CS: GO features new maps, characters, and weapons and delivers updated versions of the classic CS content (de_dust, etc.). In addition, CS: GO will introduce new gameplay modes, matchmaking, leader boards, and more.

"Counter-Strike took the gaming industry by surprise when the unlikely MOD became the most played online PC action game in the world almost immediately after its release in August 1999," said Doug Lombardi at Valve. "For the past 12 years, it has continued to be one of the most-played games in the world, headline competitive gaming tournaments and selling over 25 million units worldwide across the franchise. CS: GO promises to expand on CS' award-winning gameplay and deliver it to gamers on the PC as well as the next gen consoles and the Mac."

CS: GO is being developed by Valve in cooperation with Seattle-based Hidden Path Entertainment.

 ----- Aviso para que no se cuelguen viendo el video y despues no sea lo que buscaban.

--------------------------------------------------------------------FahRenHeit-------------------------------------------------------------

More XboxViewTV videos on MyTopTrailer: http://mytoptrailer.com/show.php?channel=XboxViewTV&vid=tzqADRiYBQ8

ABOUT THIS GAME
------------------------------------
Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS: GO) is an online FPS based game currently in development by Valve Software and Hidden Path Entertainment, who also co-developed Counter-Strike: Source. It is the fourth game in the Counter-Strike franchise, excluding Counter-Strike: Neo and Counter-Strike: Online.
Global Offensive is targeted for release in early 2012, and will be available for Microsoft Windows, Mac OS X, PlayStation 3 via the PlayStation Network and Xbox 360 via Xbox Live Arcade. It will contain classic content, such as old maps, and brand new maps, characters and game modes. Also, it will support matchmaking and leaderboards. Cross-platform multiplayer is confirmed between PC, Mac and PS3 players. The PS3 version will offer three control methods using the DualShock 3 controller, PlayStation Move or USB keyboard/mouse.

Counter-Strike: Global Offensive
-------------------------------------------------------
GENRE: First-Person Shooter
RELEASE DATE(S): 
+ US: Aug 21, 2012
+ EU: Aug 21, 2012
PLATFORM: XBLA (Xbox Live Arcade)
ALSO ON: PSN, PC(Steam), Mac

title: Counter-Strike Source: Rhedd's High FPS Config (for Low End Users)
description:
After you put the config file in C:\Program files\steam\steamapps\username\counter-strike source\cstrike\cfg    you need to right click on counterstrike source in your steam game library and then click properties, click set launch options and paste
 "-heapsize 1048576 -high -dxlevel 80"     without the quotes in the box then click ok and your done...

-heapsize = GBS of your RAM being used to play the game

-High = Sets the game to High Priority on your pc

-dxlevel 80 = uses Directx 8.0 Graphics on your pc (Directx 8.0 is for Low End users)

Link:
http://www.mediafire.com/?tr99ogijbqs8chl

title: Counter-Strike: Global Offensive - Rampage Achievement/Trophy Guide - BEST METHOD!
description:
Please note, if a patch to fix this is ever released, just clear your cache and get the achievement offline without downloading the update!

1) Set-up an Arms Race match against easy bots on either map.
2) Kill enemies until you reach the golden knife. (You can die as many times as you need)
3) Once you have the golden knife, switch teams, using the pause menu. You will respawn with dual barettas.
4) From here all you need to do is get 2 kills without dying. If you do die, just switch teams again and keep trying until you can string a kill with dual barettas and the knife in 1 life!
5) Achievement Unlocked

title: Counter-Strike - Global Offensive. Эволюция? (24 Августа 2012)
description:
Вот и состоялся релиз, значимость которого мы просто обязаны были оценить в прямом эфире. Пожалуй, самый культовый мультиплеерный шутер обзавелся (не)полноценным продолжением, не дождавшись нового графического поколения. Ориентированная скорее на консольщиков, чем на компьютерщиков CS:GO предлагает нам модное радиальное меню магазина (его же не выпилили с «беты»?), странный громоздкий прицел и коктейль Молотова из Left 4 Dead... Короче, сам бог велел, да и нет ничего лучше, чем зарубиться во что-нибудь вместе в пятницу вечером в ночном эфире. Во всяком случае, так посчитали Максим Кулаков и Константин Тростенюк.

Стримы в прямом эфире смотрим здесь - http://stopgame.ru/

Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS: GO) will expand upon the team-based action gameplay that it pioneered when it was launched 12 years ago.

CS: GO features new maps, characters, and weapons and delivers updated versions of the classic CS content (de_dust, etc.). In addition, CS: GO will introduce new gameplay modes, matchmaking, leader boards, and more.

"Counter-Strike took the gaming industry by surprise when the unlikely MOD became the most played online PC action game in the world almost immediately after its release in August 1999," said Doug Lombardi at Valve. "For the past 12 years, it has continued to be one of the most-played games in the world, headline competitive gaming tournaments and selling over 25 million units worldwide across the franchise. CS: GO promises to expand on CS' award-winning gameplay and deliver it to gamers on the PC as well as the next gen consoles and the Mac."

CS: GO is being developed by Valve in cooperation with Seattle-based Hidden Path Entertainment.

CPU: 3.0+ Dual Core CPU

Graphics: 512 MB with Shader Model 4.0 Support

title: Counter Strike 1.6 cs_estate Gungame Playthrough 2
description:
A demo of me playing the gungame mod for CS 1.6. The map is cs_estate. 

I am using a custom mod with hi-poly player and weapon models, custom sounds and sprites including a modified HUD.

If anyone would like to try out the models, sounds, and sprites that I use in this video you can download it from the following link.

http://www.mediafire.com/?86g9o89e8j6zhb8

This pack is intended for Condition Zero, but can also be used for 1.6 since both games use the goldsource engine. You will just have 2 extra player models that 1.6 won't use. If you want to use them, just rename them to one of the other models.

I also made a Counterstrike 1.6 version that uses some of the same models, but I tried to use models intended for 1.6 where possible. There aren't as many quality models available for 1.6 as there are for CZ.

You can download the 1.6 version at the following link.

http://www.mediafire.com/?p973118aakcpv27

title: Counter-Strike 1.6 - We won't forget
description:

So a friend of mine (kubia, maybe you know him) some days ago asked if I missed 1.6, and i started to watch all kind of old videos regarding streams, and I eventually decided to make a compilation of all the awesome i watched. I think it's pretty good to be honest. We can stop playing, but one thing i'm sure, we WON'T forget all the good moments we have spent on this game, playing and watching it.

I hope you like as much as I do :)

So guys, what's your favorite moment in CS 1.6? For me it's probably zonic vs mtw, or walle vs d2x (didn't include it because i wanted a full video with commentary). Tell me in the comments! 

_____________

title: Counter Strike 1.6, Gameplay [Parte 1] HD
description:
Parte 2 + Mods: https://youtu.be/pxiLWSK0lHE

Después de una semana sin subir vídeos, Hoy subí el Gameplay del juego Counter Strike 1.6 HD. Les dejo info del juego:

Counter-Strike es un juego de tipo multijugador (ya sea en LAN o en línea). Es una modificación completa del juego Half-Life, realizada por Minh Le y Jess Cliffe quienes lanzaron la primera versión el 18 de junio de 1999. La última versión del juego es el Counter-Strike Online (versión asiática licenciada por Valve), que desde su salida oficial el 15 de septiembre de 2008 ha cosechado un éxito fenomenal en Internet, haciendo de él el juego de acción en primera persona en línea más jugado en el mundo, ante juegos más recientes, como su nueva versión, Counter-Strike: Source (o CS: S) basado en el motor Source el cual se ha desarrollado para el juego Half-Life 2. Hoy en día, es también jugable en GNU/Linux mediante Wine o en Macintosh OS X.
El 12 de agosto de 2011 fue anunciada una nueva entrega de la saga Counter-Strike, llamada Counter-Strike: Global Offensive. Fue lanzada a la venta el 21 de agosto de 2012.

title: Counter-Strike Online 2 Трейлер '2012' HD
description:
http://hdtrailer.ru - Сайт канала 
http://youtube.ru/AHTIKIJIEP - Кино-трейлеры
http://vkontakte.ru/trailershd - Группа Вконтакте

Год: 2012
Разработчик: Nexon Corporation
Жанр игры: Шутер от первого лица
Издатель: Valve Corporation
Платформа: Microsoft Windows

Геймплей: Counter-Strike Online содержит различные сетевые режимы игры, как взятые с предыдущих игр серии, так и полностью новые:
Classic- стандартный режим, как и в Counter Strike 1.6.
Deathmatch - матч, в котором каждый выступает за себя.
Team Deathmatch - матч команда на команду.
Jump - режим, в котором нужно очень много прыгать, чтобы добраться до конца карты.
Survival - режим, в котором нужно убивать зомби на замкнутой местности, враги появляются постоянно.
Zombie - режим в котором все игроки должны продержаться под натиском зомби (которые в своё время, тоже являются игроками).
Vip - этот режим аналог того, что было в CS 1.6.
Alien Zombie Survival - Тот же Survival, но с прохождением.
Soccer - режим, при котором команды фактически играют в футбол. Для этого режима существует несколько моделей футболистов в футболках красного и синего цветов.

Особенности игры: В Counter-Strike Online новое оружие нужно покупать в магазине оружия. Часть оружия можно купить за очки, заработанные во время игры, а часть за Cash — эквивалент реальных денег. В разных версиях игры присутствует разное количество оружия продаваемого за реальные деньги.

П.С. Картинка на привью, нам очень понравилась, так что можете считать, что мы ей просто поделились.

http://hdtrailer.ru/game-trailers/shooter/644-counter-strike-online-2 - ссылка на этот трейлер, на нашем сайте.

title: Counter-Strike: Deleted Scenes - Rise Hard speedrun
description:
Rise Hard IL in 5:56 by coolkid 
5:58 (50.1%) faster than marshmellow 

IL (Individual Level) run means that this video was done in one go without using any kind of saves.

There is some sound sync issues in the beginning but it gets better as it proceeds.

http://speeddemosarchive.com/CounterStrikeCZDS.html

Author's comments: 
Oh man, I actually managed to get a decent run of this level before Recoil and Building Recon? I was definitely not expecting that. This could potentially be 10-15 seconds faster or so but it's extremely hard to even finish a run. In fact, I believe that this is the only time where I actually managed to complete the level in one go. The first indoors area was definitely where I reset the most (usually by dying). I blow up the turrets by throwing smoke grenades at 'em instead of using RC bombs. The most random part was at the helicopter area; there's an AWP guy on the upper ledge who killed me in about 95% of the attempts after the boost. This level much harder to run than what it might seem! If you lower your framerate (fps_max 30) you'll skip the freeze trigger before the knife duel, very useful! I sort of choked at the end of the level but I'm just glad that I managed to finish within a good time range. 

Done 2012-10-02

Suscribete a nuestro canal y entérate de todos los juegos que están saliendo en la actualidad, en el encontraras: Análisis, Noticias, Gamplay, Juagos Gratuitos, etc. 

Counter-Strike es un videojuego de disparos en primera persona multijugador (ya sea en LAN o en línea). Es una modificación completa del juego Half-Life, realizada por Minh Le y Jess Cliffe, quienes lanzaron la primera versión el 18 de junio de 1999. La última versión del juego es el Counter-Strike: Global Offensive, una de las versiones del juego más jugado en el mundo, ante juegos más recientes, como la versión Counter-Strike: Source, basado en el motor Source, desarrollado para el juego Half-Life 2. Hoy en día, es también jugable en GNU/Linux, Macintosh OS X y Windows XP, Vista, y 7 desde la plataforma Steam.

title: Counter-Strike 1.6 und Steam nativ unter Linux Ubuntu 12.10
description:
Vor einer Woche hat Valve über die Steam-Beta für Linux Counter-Strike 1.6 nativ auf unserem geliebten Betriebssystem herausgebracht.
Das musste ich natürlich gleich mal anspielen und habe das auch direkt für euch aufgenommen.

Da ich auf die Schnelle kein Programm gefunden habe, das OpenGL Spiele im Fullscreen Modus aufnehmen kann, habe ich das einfach mal im windowed mode gemacht.

Fazit:
Klappt super, fühlt sich gut an, und obwohl ich das Video aufgenommen habe, hatte ich eigentlich durchgehend die 100fps.
Kein Unterschied mehr zu Windows.
Als nächstes werde ich Team Fortress 2 ausprobieren, danach Left4Dead2, und dann kann man ja schon hoffen, dass CS:GO und Dota2, die auch auf der Source-Engine basieren, ebenfalls noch portiert werden.

title: GET BACK THE OLD COUNTER STRIKE 1.6 [2013 STEAM UPDATE]
description:
This video is about how to get back the old version (2009) of counter strike 1.6 in steam since the last update (14th feb. 2013) or you can use this tutorial to avoid the "OpenGL" Problem

1st : Disable Steam's auto-update for Counter Strike 1.6

2nd : Download the old Counter Strike 1.6 package

http://www.mediafire.com/?5ky6nc3pqa65raj

extract it via winrar then copy and past it's content to your Counter Strike directory

Default directory (after update) : C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\common\Half-Life

3rd : Reboot Steam, the run Counter Strike 1.6
Normally, an error window should pop up, just click "OK"

Song Name : Choosin - Wiz Khalifa feat. Curren$y & Rick Ross
Enjoy ^^

title: Como jogar pelo sistema MatchMaking do Counter Strike: Global Offensive
description:
Vídeo simples com passo-a-passo de como usar o sistema matchmaking do Counter Strike: Global Offensive. Infelizmente a Valve não tem servidores no Brasil, mas da pra brincar nos servidores 'rankeados' deles fora do Brasil com um ping minimo de 150.
Jogando pelo MM, você ganha medalha, sobe o rank e etc.
Lembre-se, nunca saia de uma partida em andamento, ao aceitar uma partida você estará se comprometendo a jogar todo o jogo que pode durar até 90 minutos. Se sair, você será banido e não poderá jogar usando o MM por um tempo determinado pelo sistema.

Não esqueçam de alterar o limite de ping como mostra no vídeo!

OBS: Para alguns isso pode ser um vídeo idiota, mas tem muita gente que ainda não sabe como jogar ou nunca jogou.

title: Estreno juego de las Malvinas Argentinas (mapa counter strike)
description:
En honor a nuestros soldados que dieron la vida en las malvinas lanzan un mapa para counter strike simulando los echos de ese entonces.. Mas info abajo... 

Una empresa local creó una versión del conocido videogame "Counter Strike", pero que sitúa el escenario bélico en las Islas Malvinas, durante el conflicto que protagonizaran la Argentina y Gran Bretaña en el año 1982.
    

Las Islas Malvinas, el escenario del juego de Dattatec.
La firma argentina Dattatec creó un videojuego que se sitúa en tiempo y espacio en la guerra de Malvinas. Entre otras cosas, el titulo replica lugares emblemáticos de las islas, como el cementerio y la oficina de correos.

"Counter Strike" llegó a las Islas Malvinas.
"El proyecto está teniendo una muy buena repercusión", señaló Fernando Llorente, representante de Dattatec, empresa afincada en la ciudad de Rosario. Aunque reconoció que el escenario que aborda puede generar cierta polémica.

Al respecto, Llorente señaló: "Nuestra idea no es provocar a nadie, pero pensamos que la temàtica puede llegar a sensibilizar sobre un tema importante". "El reclamo por la soberanía de las Islas Malvinas es un deseo compartido por 40 millones de argentinos y no es nuestra intención ofender o faltar el respeto".
 
En defensa del contenido del videojuego, Llorente explicó que "en el mensaje final del juego aparece la la leyenda: 'Islas Malvinas, olvidarlas nunca, olvidarlos jamás'". Asimismo, esta singular versión de "Counter Strike" da la posibilidad de que los soldados argentinos recuperen el archipiélago, algo que no ocurrió en la realidad.
 
En la acción del juego, como ocurre con todas las demás versiones de "Counter Strike", se enfrentan una banda de "terroristas", en este caso los británicos, con un grupo de "policías", los argentinos.

title: Counter Strike- Global Defensive
description:
we fight the good fight and take on the bad guys
players are: IIDwellerII, Legit/Henry, Sperse/Kendal, IITheDoctorII

What is Counter Strike Global Offensive?
Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (abbreviated as CS:GO) is an online first-person shooter developed by Valve Corporation and Hidden Path Entertainment, who also maintained Counter-Strike: Source after its release. It is the fourth game in the Counter-Strike franchise, excluding Counter-Strike Neo and Online.
Global Offensive was released on August 21, 2012, and made available for Microsoft Windows and OS X on Steam, Xbox Live Arcade, and a US-only version on PlayStation Network. It features classic content, such as revamped versions of classic maps; as well as brand new maps, characters and game modes. Cross-platform multiplayer was planned between Windows, OS X and PSN players, but was ultimately limited to Windows and Mac OS because of the differences in update-frequency between systems. The PSN version offers three input control methods, which include using either the DualShock 3 controller, PlayStation Move or USB keyboard/mouse. Like the previous games in the series, Global Offensive is an objective-based multiplayer first-person shooter. Each player joins either the Terrorist or Counter-Terrorist team and attempts to complete objectives or eliminate the enemy team. The game operates in short rounds that end when all players on one side are dead or a team's objective is completed. For most game modes, once a player dies, they must wait until the round ends to respawn. Players purchase weapons and equipment at the beginning of every round with money awarded based on their performance. Completing objectives or killing enemies earns the player money while negative actions, like killing a teammate or hostage, takes money away from the player. In addition, when a round ends all players receive some amount of money, with players on the winning team receiving substantially more.
Global Offensive adds new weapons and equipment not seen in previous installments, most notably the firebomb for each side (Molotovs for Terrorists and incendiary grenades for Counter-Terrorists). These temporarily cover a small area in fire, dealing damage to anyone passing through.

Creator(s) of the map: Cuniczek

A newer, or preferably another version of minecraft for Zombie Escape. Minecraft Adventures features different levels, special items and fresh, new colors with real minecraft player skins! The map design is incredibly accurate to the real game and satisfies every aspect of the zombie escape gameplay. Also, it's quite challenging, making it a must-have played for every ZE player. Have fun!


PARTS

* First playround: 0:00 - 04:12 
* Second playround: 04:13 - 08:17
* Third playround: 08:18 - 11:15
* Last playround: 11:16 - End of video

* Funny Fail: 10:36


General info in-game:

* All models WERE HD (World views). This WAS for the quality of the game, as the standard models are (still) very undetailed. The STEAMPIPE UPDATE BROKE WORLD SKINS and as such are currently missing in any of my incoming videos after this one. I'm sorry for that and this will be fixed as soon as Valve updates CS:S to work properly again!
* M3, Deagle, AWP, AK47 & M249 aren' the original versions, this is due to the need of some change over the default skins after all this time.
* Both CT's and T's packs are different, they are very highly detailed models. Again because of the poor standard quality
* At last, the in-game options are all highest, except for Anti-aliasing, which is x4 instead of x8 for faster performance.


GAMEPLAY MODE: Zombie Escape

* ze stands for Zombie Escape, and is one of the most funniest mods in css that you can find. The game starts with equal teams in T's and CT's and after 8-10 seconds, one player turns into a zombie and must try to hit other players with his single knife... With a bit of luck, he can already hit 3-5 people in a row, and then the epidemy continiues. Otherwise, you have zombie-hunters, which try to kill the first zombie for a quick win (=boring). Zombies have around 2500-3000 health, players the traditional 100hp. Humans must survive to keep the human race alive, otherwise they will be destroyed for an unending life of torment! Have fun!

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

title: Como Arrumar o BUG da tela preta no Counter - Strike 1.6 - HD
description:
Leia a Descrição

Como arrumar o bug da tela preta no Counter - Strike :

1º Passo - Vá até a área de trabalho , após isso em cima do icone do Counter - Strike , clique com o botão direito do mouse e vá em PROPRIEDADES , a seguir em destino você vai ter que alterar tudo para isto : "C:\Program Files\Valve\hl.exe" -game cstrike -d3d -32bpp -w 800 -h 600 [ COM ASPAS E TUDO ] 

2º Passo - Após isso , vocês vão no Iniciar e terão que escrever REGEDIT , após abrir uma janela , vocês vão nas seguintes pastas abaixo : 

1º -  " HKEY_CURRENT_USER "
2º -  " Software "
3º -  " Valve "
4º -  " Half - Life "
5º -  " Settings  "

3º Passo - Quando você clica na pasta " Settings " vai aparecer vários arquivos do lado direito da sua tela ... Nesses arquivos você vai ter que procurar 2 arquivos , ScreenHeight e o ScreenWidth

4º Passo - Quando você achar os 2 arquivos vocês terão que alterar eles ... Clique 2 vezes em cima do " ScreenHeight " e altere os numeros para 360 ... Já no arquivo " ScreenWidth " você terá que alterar para 460 . Após isto você pode fechar tudo e abrir seu Counter - Strike Normalmente , pois pegará sem nenhum problema !!

• Gostou ? Curte e Comente ... Pois vou responder a todas as perguntas !!

• Se Inscreva-se no meu Canal : http://www.youtube.com/ForseGamesOficial

title: Counter-Strike Football League Season 2 Promo
description:
Hello subscribers, this is my newest work, made for my friend from the US. It's a promo video for an American Football Mod league all the info about it is bellow.
-------------------------------------------------------------
Sign up on the forums at www.CSafm.com
CS 1.6 Server IP: 68.232.169.113:27015

Season 2 will begin on August 2nd.

6 teams will occupy a 6 week season.
Each team will play 1 game per week, except the first week where each team will play 2 games.
There will be 3 divisions with 2 teams per division.
The first place team from each division will make the playoffs.
One wildcard team will also make the playoffs.
The wildcard is determined by the win-loss record then the head-to-head record if necessary.
Playoffs will be two weeks long, rendering 8 weeks in total.

The player draft will take place on Saturday, July 27th.
The 7-round draft will be broadcasted on twitch.tv

Check out our channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/csfootballmod

title: PC Longplay [330] Counter Strike Condition Zero
description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Frederikct112

Hello everybody im back here again with another longplay. This time i thought to myself that i needed to do a good FPS game so i later came up with the idea of doing CS:CZ. Now im going to be honest here: Im not good at FPS games. Sure, i did L4D2/L4D but those games are easy compared to CS. I would say i did pretty good in this longplay, though i died a few times and yeah sure, my aim is not the best, but i did it, thus only on Easy Mode. And i am sorry for sometimes going a little fast in the buy menu, its just a habit i have developed over time playing CS a long time.

STORY/INFO ABOUT GAME
Counter-Strike: Condition Zero (CZ or CS:CZ) is a multiplayer video game and the follow-up to Counter-Strike. The game was released in 2004 using the GoldSrc Half-Life engine. CS:CZ features a multiplayer mode, which features updated character models, textures, maps and other graphical tweaks. Unlike other Counter-Strike games, Condition Zero also contains a single-player mission pack with the player playing as counter-terrorist alongside bots. The player unlocks maps and more effective bot teammates as he or she passes certain requirements for each map while playing as a counter terrorist. These requirements include targets such as "kill 3 enemies with a Bullpup" or "win a round in 60 seconds". Counter-Strike bots are a prominent part of Condition Zero gameplay. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!

De sNaTe CNZ
Chicos ocupo su apoyo si tienen el Counter strike 1.6 como no steam o steam como sea porfavor metanse al servidor y cada dia 15 de cada mes se regala admin al 1 jugador del rank :) aprovechen Servidor de Counter Strike 1.6 [SteamGameR] 24/7 [Troble in Terrorist Town][Mx] IP:63.209.33.117:27035 De que trata El modo de juego se basa en que hay un grupo pequeño de traidores y otro de detectives, paso a explicar la función de cada uno. Traidores Los traidores deben asesinar a todos sin ser detectados, ellos saben quienes son porque solo entre ellos mismos se ven un “circulo” rojo que les parpadea alrededor del cuerpo de sus compañeros. También al ver el score (TAB), verán que son CTs junto a otros que dicen “VIP”, los VIPs son los DETECTIVES, el resto, sus compañeros. Tocando la letra “o”, o escribiendo /buy en say o say_team, pueden comprar cosas especiales para traidores. Para usar lo que han comprado, deben usar el botón de la linterna (F). Entre los traidores pueden usar un canal de micrófono especial, bindeando una letra “+specialvoice” Detectives Los detectives tienen métodos especiales para detectar al traidor, por ejemplo, cuando ven un cuerpo, deben analizar al cuerpo, buscando en el mismo hasta que diga un mensaje en el medio “No identificado”, al verlo, tocar la E, si el cuerpo fue recientemente matado, te dirá si era Inocente o traidor Ademas tienen un shop que se abre con la letra “o”, o escribiendo /buy, al comprar algo, luego deben presionar la F para usar los elementos. Entre los detectives pueden usar un canal de micrófono especial, bindeando una letra “+specialvoice” Siempre figuran como CT y todos los ven como CTs, ademas destellan un circulo azul en su cuerpo que todos ven (a diferencia de los traidores que solo se ven entre ellos CT y el destello solo se lo ven ellos) Inocentes La tarea de los inocentes es detectar a los traidores y defender mas que nada a los detectives, ellos deben matar a la persona correcta, no poseen shop, ni nada en especial. Vale aclarar que todos se pueden matar entre todos, pero hay algo llamado “KARMA”, que arrancan con un inicial, y va aumentando si hacen las cosas bien (si matan traidores, o si matan gente los traidores), en caso contrario, te descontara KARMA. El KARMA sirve para el daño que generan las armas, cuanto mas KARMA, mas daño hará tu arma.

title: Counter strike 1.6 #1 - Przydatne komendy
description:
Cześć, dziś przedstawie Wam parę przydatnych komend w grze Counter strike 1.6, zapraszam do oglądania.

Komendy:
1. hud_fastswitch 1 - zmiana broni klawiszami bez akceptacji myszką (tzw, szybka zmiana broni)
2. cl_dynamiccrosshair "0" - podczas biegu celownik nie zwiększa się ale również nie zmniejsza przy kucaniu
3. cl_allowdownload "0" - nie ściągają się nam żadne pliki z serwer / aby włączyć wpisujemy liczbę 1
4. net_graph 3 - pokazuje nam standardowo w dolnym prawym rogu informacje dotyczące ilości fps, loss itd ( aby wyłączyć wpisujemy 0 )
5. _cl_autowepswitch 0 - po wpisaniu tej komendy broń lepsza nie będzie nam wpadała
  w ręce kiedy na nią najdziemy lub kiedy kupimy (paka również)
6. cl_crosshair_color RRR GGG BBB - Zmiana koloru celownika
7. cl_weather 0 -wyłącza efekty mapy (deszcz,wiatr)

More information about the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS:GO) game:
Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS:GO) expands upon the team-based action gameplay that the franchise pioneered when it was launched 12 years ago.
CS:GO features new maps, characters, and weapons and delivers updated versions of the classic CS content (de_dust, etc.). In addition, CS:GO introduces new gameplay modes, matchmaking, leader boards, and more.
Classic: Competitive
This is the classic gameplay that made Counter-Strike famous. Queue up and join a 5v5 best-of-30 match using standard competitive Counter-Strike rules on one of the classic maps. You can join a match on your own, or form a team and enter a match as a unit.
Classic: Casual
Ready to play some Counter-Strike, but don't want to commit to a full match? Find a casual match and play at your own pace. In Casual mode, players automatically receive body armor and defusal kits and gain bonus rewards for kills.
Demolition
In demolition mode, players take turns attacking and defending a single bombsite in a series of maps designed for fast-paced gameplay. Players are automatically granted a starting weapon, and advance through a sequence of firearms when they register a kill. If you're up to the challenge, you can try to register a kill each round and reach the ultimate weapons, powerful sniper rifles!
Arms Race
Arms race is a gun-progression mode featuring instant respawning and a ton of close-quarter combat. Players gain new weapons immediately after registering a kill as they work their way through each weapon in the game. Get a kill with the final weapon, a golden knife, and win the match.
( Description via - http://bit.ly/15sOzjH )

* Map Info *

Creator(s) of the map: Subdelt@

Finally the moment arrived when Unreal Tournament made its introduction to Zombie Escape, thanks to Subdelt@, a good friend of mine as mapper and ZE player! UT2004 Convoy is based on a real-existent multiplayer map of Unreal Tournament 2004 itself, and has been carefully rebuilt into the Source Engine. There are many different hold spots, and punctual teamwork is required to win the map. Difficulties are progressivly difficult, but novice already proved to be difficult on its own, though we did hold out as you can see. You cannot 'not have played' this map, it's masterpiece of brushworks and props, combined with fun and challenging gameplay, so gab your hands on it, and test it out on any server! Have fun!


General info in-game:

* All models WERE HD (World views). This WAS for the quality of the game, as the standard models are (still) very undetailed. The STEAMPIPE UPDATE BROKE WORLD SKINS and as such are currently missing in any of my incoming videos after this one. I'm sorry for that and this will be fixed as soon as Valve updates CS:S to work properly again!
* M3, Deagle, AWP, AK47 & M249 aren' the original versions, this is due to the need of some change over the default skins after all this time.
* Both CT's and T's packs are different, they are very highly detailed models. Again because of the poor standard quality
* At last, the in-game options are all highest, except for Anti-aliasing, which is x4 instead of x8 for faster performance.


GAMEPLAY MODE: Zombie Escape

* ze stands for Zombie Escape, and is one of the most funniest mods in css that you can find. The game starts with equal teams in T's and CT's and after 8-10 seconds, one player turns into a zombie and must try to hit other players with his single knife... With a bit of luck, he can already hit 3-5 people in a row, and then the epidemy continiues. Otherwise, you have zombie-hunters, which try to kill the first zombie for a quick win (=boring). Zombies have around 2500-3000 health, players the traditional 100hp. Humans must survive to keep the human race alive, otherwise they will be destroyed for an unending life of torment! Have fun!
